graph TB
    subgraph "Training Operator Component"
        Controller[Training Operator Controller<br/>Port: 8080/TCP metrics<br/>Port: 8081/TCP health]
        PyTorchCtrl[PyTorch Controller<br/>Elastic training + HPA]
        TFCtrl[TensorFlow Controller<br/>Parameter server + workers]
        MPICtrl[MPI Controller<br/>Launcher + workers]
        XGBoostCtrl[XGBoost Controller<br/>Master + workers]
        MXNetCtrl[MXNet Controller<br/>Scheduler + server + workers]
        PaddleCtrl[PaddlePaddle Controller<br/>Distributed training]
        Webhook[Webhook Server<br/>Port: 9443/TCP HTTPS]
        Metrics[Metrics Exporter<br/>Prometheus format]
        SDK[Python SDK<br/>TrainingClient API]

        Controller -->|manages| PyTorchCtrl
        Controller -->|manages| TFCtrl
        Controller -->|manages| MPICtrl
        Controller -->|manages| XGBoostCtrl
        Controller -->|manages| MXNetCtrl
        Controller -->|manages| PaddleCtrl
        Controller -->|validates| Webhook
        Controller -->|exposes| Metrics
    end

    %% CRDs
    User[Data Scientist] -->|creates via| SDK
    SDK -->|submits| PyTorchJobCR[PyTorchJob CR]
    SDK -->|submits| TFJobCR[TFJob CR]
    SDK -->|submits| MPIJobCR[MPIJob CR]
    SDK -->|submits| XGBoostJobCR[XGBoostJob CR]
    SDK -->|submits| MXJobCR[MXJob CR]
    SDK -->|submits| PaddleJobCR[PaddleJob CR]

    PyTorchJobCR -->|watched by| PyTorchCtrl
    TFJobCR -->|watched by| TFCtrl
    MPIJobCR -->|watched by| MPICtrl
    XGBoostJobCR -->|watched by| XGBoostCtrl
    MXJobCR -->|watched by| MXNetCtrl
    PaddleJobCR -->|watched by| PaddleCtrl

    %% Resources created
    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| WorkerPods[Worker Pods]
    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| Services[Services]
    PyTorchCtrl -->|creates| HPA[HorizontalPodAutoscaler]
    TFCtrl -->|creates| WorkerPods
    TFCtrl -->|creates| Services
    MPICtrl -->|creates| WorkerPods
    MPICtrl -->|creates| LauncherPod[Launcher Pod]

    %% External dependencies
    Controller -->|depends on| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API]
    Controller -->|optional| Volcano[Volcano Scheduler<br/>Gang scheduling]
    Controller -->|default| SchedulerPlugins[scheduler-plugins v0.25.7+<br/>Gang scheduling]
    Controller -->|integrates| PrometheusOp[Prometheus<br/>Metrics collection]

    %% ODH integrations
    Controller -.->|displayed in| ODHDashboard[ODH Dashboard]
    WorkerPods -.->|may use| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh]

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:3px
    style PyTorchCtrl fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style TFCtrl fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style MPICtrl fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style XGBoostCtrl fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style MXNetCtrl fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style PaddleCtrl fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333
    style SDK fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
